  "architecture_summary": "The paper studies self-supervised training of Vision Transformers in contrastive/Siamese frameworks, centered on a MoCo v3 setup with a backbone, projection head, and prediction head. It emphasizes training stability issues and shows that freezing the patch projection as a fixed random patch projection can improve stability and accuracy across several self-supervised frameworks.",
